			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="However this scene plays out, the warlock is enigmatic and self-assured - she saves players and then departs, hinting toward the help that her master can offer in other similar situations.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Players have been captured by the goblin priestess and could not escape their chains. After they rest, the priestess returns to see if they've transformed into mind flayers (as she expected) and is disappointed to see they haven't. She intends to kill them, but a warlock intervenes and saves the players, killing the priestess.&#xA;&#xA;The warlock has been sent by its master, a cambion called The Monitor, who players may have met already. " />
